Minor module: Use a database for the backend. []
    
Major module: Standard user management, authentication, users across tournaments.
◦ Users can subscribe to the website in a secure way. [D]
◦ Registered users can log in in a secure way. [D]
◦ Users can select a unique display name to play the tournaments. [D]
◦ Users can update their information. [D]
◦ Users can upload an avatar, with a default option if none is provided. [D]
◦ Users can add others as friends and view their online status. [D]
◦ User profiles display stats, such as wins and losses.
◦ Each user has a Match History including 1v1 games, dates, and relevant
details, accessible to logged-in users.